<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-10-19T03:00:00-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-10-19T03:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-19T03:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Stoke Voltaics 便携式电炊具评测</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/qSFkX-bVqp5_wAKSwLPkoLJUvsM=/0x476:5712x4284/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73663597/IMG_1690.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Stoke Voltaic Nomad 烹饪系统（左）和 Joulle 水壶。&lt;/em>; | &lt;em>;摄影：Thomas Ricker / The Verge&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;cisDOy&quot;>;有时您只需要一个便携式电炊具。也许是在一次大停电期间，每个人都挤在一起享受家庭发电站的温暖光芒。或者可能是在车尾派对或野餐中。就我而言，过去几个月我决定将货车停在任何地方，同时测试 Stoke Voltaics 的两种烹饪系统。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;6k23sI&quot;>;大多数便携式炊具由丙烷等液体燃料提供动力。它价格便宜，并且很容易在各种尺寸的罐中获得。但有时您不想面对明火、污染物以及随之而来的噪音和气味。 Stoke Voltaics 的设备由电力提供动力，可以轻松地通过太阳能发电机供电并通过太阳补充能量。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ONNRIX&quot;>;我测试了该公司的新&lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.stokevoltaics.store/products/nomad-cooking-system&quot;>;$...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24273375/stoke-voltaics -portable-electric-cookware-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24273375/stoke-voltaics-portable-electric-cookware-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24273375/stoke-voltaics-portable-electric-cookware-review</id><author><name>托马斯·瑞克</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-18T19:19:48-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-18T19:19:48-04:00</updated><title>您现在可以购买的最好的智能锁</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;亮黄色、粉色和橙色图形上的门锁&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/5dO8UhrbXIz1LtBQXXPtGHMXh8c=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/71491011/226294_Doorbell_buying_Guide_Kradtke.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;使用您可以控制的智能锁，再也不会被锁在门外通过您的手机、通过语音或只需用手指触摸即可。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23393163/best-smart-door-lock&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23393163/best-smart-door-lock" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23393163/best-smart-door-lock</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-18T18:36:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-18T18:36:54-04:00</updated><title>最适合训练和日常生活的 Garmin 手表</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;彩色背景上的几款 Garmin 手表&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/D5dtgeyIVuFtgCeI1hMNSF_9Epo=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72245384/236645_Buying_Guide_Garmin_Watches_WJoel.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Garmins 不再只是多项运动的庞然大物。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Will Joel / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Garmin 可能以其硬核健身手表而闻名，但它也提供广泛的生活方式产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-18T18:32:10-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-18T18:32:10-04:00</updated><title>企鹅兰登书屋书籍现在明确对人工智能培训说“不”</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一张有故障的铅笔在纸上书写的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/zf5YwlL7OVqe7rPn9RR6pKlBRCk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73663192/STK149_AI_Writing.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Hugo Herrera / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;1KveEQ&quot;>;图书出版商 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2013/7/1/4482980 /penguin-and-random-house-officially-merge-become-penguin-random-house&quot;>;企鹅兰登书屋&lt;/a>;正在以印刷形式表达其对人工智能培训的立场。根据 &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.thebookseller.com/news/penguin-random-house-underscores-copyright-protection-in-ai-rebuff&quot;>;来自&lt;em>;书商的报告&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>; &lt;/em >;发现&lt;a href=&quot;https://gizmodo.com/penguin-adds-a-do-not-scrape-for-ai-page-to-its-books-2000513543&quot;>;由&lt;em>;Gizmodo&lt;/em >;&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ClGkpM&quot;>;该条款还指出，企鹅兰登书屋根据欧盟法律“明确保留该作品的文本和数据挖掘例外”。 &lt;em>;书商&lt;/em>;表示&lt;em>; &lt;/em>;企鹅兰登书屋似乎是第一家在其版权页面上说明人工智能的主要出版商。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;vtOdia&quot;>;该页面上打印的内容可能是警告镜头，但它与实际情况没有什么关系...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/10/18/24273895/penguin-random-house-books-copyright-ai&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/18/24273895/penguin-random-house-books-copyright-ai" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/18/24273895/penguin-random-house-books-copyright-ai</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-18T18:23:27-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-18T18:23:27-04:00</updated><title>周五古巴全岛停电</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;人们在红绿灯关闭时过马路。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ZVy44XxMVaHoQ3JBi_HXvA44cYo=/0x0:2955x1970/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73663174/2178426888.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption >;&lt;em>;2024 年 10 月 18 日哈瓦那，由于电网故障导致全国停电，人们在红绿灯关闭时过马路。&lt;/em>; |图片来源：Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;PAAx0R&quot;>;据古巴能源部称，周五，一座大型发电厂发生故障，导致古巴全国断电。停电一直是古巴老化电网的一个反复出现的问题，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2024/10/18/world/americas/cuba-power-plant-blackout.html&quot;>;&lt; em>;《纽约时报》&lt;/em>; 报道称，&lt;/a>; 指出该国数周以来一直缺乏燃料来全面运行电网。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;903llS&quot;>;其国家电力系统于 11 日完全断开。当地时间上午 :00，能源部&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/EnergiaMinasCub/status/1847315612738978114&quot;>;在 X 上发布消息&lt;/a>;。 4:00 左右，该部&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/EnergiaMinasCub/status/1847373068710343117&quot;>;报告&lt;/a>;部分地区已实现微电网系统运行。&lt;/ p>; &lt;div id=&quot;zTWD9Q&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;es&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>;Proceso de Restauración &lt;br>;del SEN &lt;br>;✅️ Ya tenemosgeneración parcial en能源。 &lt;br>;✅️ Se conectan las Primeras cargas para llegar con energía a las termoeléctricas。&lt;br>;✅️ Ya funcionan los micro sistemas electricos en &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/hashtag/VillaClara?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src =twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;#VillaClara&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/hashtag/Holgu%C3%ADn?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;#Holguín&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/hashtag/Granma?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;#...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/18/24273905/cuba-power-outage-energy-crisis&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/18/24273905/cuba-power-outage-energy-crisis" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/18/24273905/cuba-power-outage-energy-crisis</id><author><name>贾斯汀·卡尔玛</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-18T18:15:04-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-18T18:15:04-04:00</updated><title>首席执行官表示，通用汽车今年将开始在电动汽车上赚钱</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;陈列室里的蓝色雪佛兰 Equinox 电动汽车。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JETp4iU5sJ4qr60xRvyoajfiMW4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73663160/226268_CHEVY_EV_LINEUP_PHO_ahawkins_ 0007.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;雪佛兰 Equinox 是最便宜的电动汽车之一。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Andrew Hawkins / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Av8Taf&quot;>;通用汽车将于今年年底开始通过其电动汽车赚钱，&lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2022/11/17/23464509/general-motors-ev-profit-1-million-annual-2025&quot;>;按计划进行&lt;/a>;&lt;strong>;，&lt;/strong>;首席执行官玛丽·巴拉&lt; a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2024/10/17/business/gm-electric-vehicles-mary-barra.html&quot;>;告诉&lt;em>;纽约时报&lt;/em>;&lt;/a >;。博拉还告诉该刊物，通用汽车仍将在 2035 年之前逐步停止内燃机汽车的销售，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/28/22254116/general-motors-carbon- neutral-vow-2040-tailpipe-emissions-ev&quot;>;2021 年设定的目标&lt;/a>;以及到 2040 年实现碳中和的承诺。通用汽车在 2023 年底面临影响其电池生产的制造和供应链问题，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/24/23930143/gm-delay-ev-chevy-equinox-silverado-sierra-q3-earnings&quot;>;推迟了一系列电动车型的推出&lt;/a>;，但巴拉说这些问题已经解决了。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;BW3AFC&quot;>;目前，特斯拉在美国销售的电动汽车最多，并且仅靠它们就盈利了&lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2021/7/26/22594778/tesla-q2-2021-earnings-revenue-profit-credits-emissions-bitcoin&quot;>;自 2021 年起&lt;/a>;。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/25/24140033/ford-q1-2024-earnings-ev-hybrid-loss-sale&quot;>;第二大&lt;/a>;电动汽车生产商在该国是福特，但它一直在发布 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/21/24225177/ford-electric-vehicle-cancellations-delays-suv-t3-pickup&quot; >;第一次损失超过十亿美元&lt;/a>;...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/18/24273630/gm- ev-profitability-viability-2024-barra&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/18/24273630/gm-ev-profitability-viability-2024-barra" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/18/24273630/gm-ev-profitability-viability-2024-barra</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-18T18:07:03-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-18T18:07:03-04:00</updated><title>最好的预算机器人真空吸尘器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;各种扫地机器人插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HibcNT_fQEjjbn2ocPGsJMt6h-E=/0x0:2040x